## Purpose

This license allows you to use this software for non-commercial purposes for free. To use this software for commercial purposes, you must either buy a commercial license or use it for a 30-day trial period.

## Agreement

In order to receive this license, you must agree to its rules. The rules of this license are both obligations of your agreement with the licensor and conditions to your license. You must not do anything with this software that triggers a rule that you cannot or will not follow.

## Rules

### 1. Trials

If you are using this software for a commercial purpose, you may do so for a 30-day trial period. After the trial period, you must either stop using the software for a commercial purpose or buy a commercial license from the licensor.

### 2. Commercial Purposes

For the purposes of this license, "commercial purposes" means any use of the software for profit or on behalf of a business that is not a non-profit organization.

### 3. Non-Commercial Purposes

You may use this software for any non-commercial purpose for free. "Non-commercial purposes" include personal use, educational use, and use by non-profit organizations.

### 4. Notices

You must ensure that any copy of this software that you provide to others includes this license and any copyright or other proprietary notices that the licensor has included.

## Excuses

If you fail to follow a rule of this license, your license is automatically terminated. However, the licensor may excuse your failure if you fix the problem within 30 days of becoming aware of it.

